GateDocument.TextWithNodes: Actinomycetes (actinobacteria) are getting more and more recognized as a natural source for new drug exploration. In order to find new lead compounds, the diversity and selected bioactivities of cultured actinomycetes in the Baltic Sea (Germany) were investigated.
